VignetteBuilder: knitr
Description: Provides functions to apply Spatial Fuzzy c-means 
    Algorithm, visualize and interpret results. This method is 
    well suited when the user wants to analyze data with a 
    fuzzy clustering algorithm and to account for the spatial dimension of 
    the dataset. Tests for estimating the spatial consistency and classification 
    quality are proposed in addition.
